## Brand & Design System

### Color Palette

```ts
// /src/theme/theme.ts
primary:   '#2E7D32'   // Southwest Greens dark green
secondary: '#81C784'   // Light green accent
neutral:   '#F5F5F5'   // Background gray
text:      '#1A1A1A'   // Near-black body text
warning:   '#F9A825'   // Amber — quotes pending, tasks overdue
error:     '#C62828'   // Red — lost leads, critical flags
info:      '#1565C0'   // Blue — informational callouts
```

### Typography

- Base font size: `14px`
- Font family: `Inter, sans-serif` (set in MUI theme)
- Page titles: `h5` variant (MUI Typography)
- Section headers: `h6` variant
- Table headers: `body2` + `fontWeight: 600`
- Labels / metadata: `caption` variant

### Spacing

- Use MUI's `spacing()` system (base 8px). Never hard-code pixel values in `sx`.
- Section padding: `p: 3` (24px)
- Card padding: `p: 2` (16px)
- Gap between stat cards: `gap: 2`

