| Location / Region | `MapPin` |
| Add / Create | `Plus` |
| Edit | `Pencil` |
| Delete | `Trash2` |
| Search | `Search` |
| Filter | `SlidersHorizontal` |
| Dashboard | `LayoutDashboard` |
